creative housing options.

14
00:00:25,944 --> 00:00:28,328
Baby, my mom is not
staying at a hotel.

15
00:00:28,330 --> 00:00:30,820
Or our storage unit.

16
00:00:30,845 --> 00:00:32,316
Why can't we borrow
your air mattress?

17
00:00:32,317 --> 00:00:33,816
