of my generosity, Barney?

47
00:01:45,407 --> 00:01:48,391
Or should I say,
"Borrow-ney"?

48
00:01:48,393 --> 00:01:49,609
You should
never say that.

49
00:01:49,611 --> 00:01:51,161
And I think he's out
with Patrice.

50
00:01:51,163 --> 00:01:53,363
