Hang up,
you little bitch!

83
00:03:00,064 --> 00:03:01,564
Over-correction.

84
00:03:01,566 --> 00:03:02,999
Yeah. And it's not just
relationships.

85
00:03:03,001 --> 00:03:05,235
Remember when that
comedy club owner told Marshall

86
00:03:05,237 --> 00:03:07,187
that his "funny fish names"
stand-up act

