148
00:05:37,646 --> 00:05:39,179
is always there.

149
00:05:39,181 --> 00:05:40,230
Okay?
Okay.

150
00:05:40,232 --> 00:05:41,682
And that's
why I need

151
00:05:41,684 --> 00:05:44,268
